<br>
I'm quite often asked to attend pickup dragon raids when I play my enchanter.  Thank god I turn them all down. <br>
<br>
&quot;so and so tells you, Hey, we need enchanters on this pickup raid, would you like to attend? We need you, but you can't roll on loot, because you're not 50 yet, care to join?&quot;<br>
